<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>Select the <b class="Bold">Allow Product Notification</b> checkbox to enable the Message, Start and End date fields. Enter a Start and End date for the notifications and the message content. The Message content is limited to 400 characters. Email and message center communications is sent per agent per day regarding all pending activities for the product indicated for the date range specified. The UI enables the message if the Allow Product Notifications checkbox is selected and values exist in  the following fields: Message, Start date, and End date. Since this notification lives at the product level, the notification applies for all locked activities for all distributors who use this product. Carriers need to deploy the Product Configuration to add the product notification. Only carriers can enable and update this option and associated Message and Start and End date fields. Clear the checkbox to clear the Message, Start and End fields. Emails and Message Center notifications for the Product Notification are added to the Audit report for the activity. The user will see the Product Notification message when opening the Activity. </body>
</html>